Package org.example.exception

package org.example.exception
This package contains the exception classes. These classes are used to provide exception handling for the game.
  • The classes in this package are:
    • GlobalExceptionHandler: Global exception handler for the application.
    • InvalidPlayerException: Exception to handle invalid player.
    • InvalidPurchaseException: Exception to handle invalid purchase.
